                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-box ftco-animate">
                    <p style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #d582c3; text-transform: uppercase;font-style: italic;">Happy Hotel</p>
                    <p>"We are committed to bringing you a wonderful stay experience at our hotel. Dedicated service, clean and comfortable environment are what we aim for, so that you can enjoy Enjoy a perfect and memorable vacation."</p>
